OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy with rain or
OL,6,Fshowers, some heavy, during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Rain will clear to showers
OL,8,Fduring the morning, these becoming
OL,9,Ffrequent during the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThe evening will see some
OL,12,Fbright spells and showers. These
OL,13,Fshowers will clear form the late
OL,14,Fevening and clear spells will increase
OL,15,Ftowards the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FThe morning will be dry with
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells. A few showers
OL,19,Fbuild in the afternoon and cloud
OL,20,Fincreases towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
