OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of rain, some heavy,
OL,7,Fturning showery later Saturday.
OL,8,FFurther showery rain Sunday. Rain
OL,9,Fclears Monday morning, leaving the
OL,10,Fafternoon dry and bright.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
